{"id":544278216,"lang":"cpp","time":"6 months, 2 weeks","timestamp":1629940373,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"3 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/544278216/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Sqrt(x)","memory":"6 MB","code":"class Solution {\npublic:\n    int mySqrt(int x) {\n        if(x==0 || x==1)return x;\n        int l=1,h=x/2;\n        while(l<=h){\n            int m=l+(h-l)/2,q=x/m;\n            if(m==q) return m;\n            else if(m<q) l=m+1;\n            else h=m-1;\n        }\n        return h;\n    }\n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"sqrtx"}
